description: CIBL, Inc. provides high speed broadband and communications services. The company offers its services to an approximately 35 -square-mile area in northern New Hampshire, including the Omni Mount Washington Hotel and Resort, The Mount Washington Cog Railway, and the summit of Mount Washington, New Hampshire's highest mountain. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Reno, Nevada.
ceo: Mr. Mario Joseph Gabelli C.F.A., CFA
